Alembic migrations for art-school-management.

Generate a new revision after model changes:
    cd backend && alembic revision --autogenerate -m "description"

Apply:
    cd backend && alembic upgrade head

Note: M1 currently uses Base.metadata.create_all() in app.main lifespan + seed.py
for first-time setup; switch to alembic-only after schema stabilizes.
